  DisplayName: Hold Public Policy Debates
  Description: The people deserve a unifying set of values that respect cultural
    diversity and worker's rights, but that framework must be established by the
    people themselves. Public policy debates over the rights and freedoms we are
    fighting for will help legitimize our cause and truly democratize the process
    by which we organize our members.
